---
import Layout from '../layouts/Layout.astro';
import Navbar from '../components/Navbar.jsx';
import Footer from '../components/Footer.astro';
import BreadcrumbSchema from '../components/BreadcrumbSchema.astro';
import FAQSchema from '../components/FAQSchema.astro';
import { BOOKING_URL, PHONE } from '../lib/site.js';

const faqs = [
  { q: 'Why don’t you list exact prices?', a: 'Because exact prices belong to exact sites. The from-numbers are real: builds start at $3,800 + GST and care starts at $149 a month + GST. What your site lands at depends on what it needs to do, and I’d rather price your actual job than sell you a package that half fits. You’ll have your number in writing before anything begins.' },
  { q: 'Is there a cheaper option?', a: 'No, and that’s deliberate. If budget is the deciding factor, I’m not your builder, and I’ll happily point you at good DIY options. No hard feelings.' },
  { q: 'What about the audit credit?', a: 'Build with me within 90 days of your audit landing in your inbox and the full $997 comes off your build price. No conditions. After 90 days the audit stands as its own piece of work.' },
  { q: 'Can I pause or cancel?', a: 'Pause anytime, no penalty, site stays live. Cancel with 30 days notice and everything comes with you.' },
  { q: 'What if I don’t love the site?', a: 'Full refund of your setup fee, minus card processing (about 3%) and domain costs. You see the complete site before the subscription starts.' },
  { q: 'Do you work with clients outside New Zealand?', a: 'Yes. Based in Whangārei, working worldwide, everything remote. You pay in NZ dollars and your bank handles the conversion.' },
  { q: 'Why is there a monthly fee at all?', a: 'Because a website isn’t a thing you buy once. It’s a thing that runs, and things that run need someone watching them. The monthly means that someone is me, and you never think about it.' },
];
---

<Layout
  title="Website Pricing NZ | From $3,800 + GST | YourHQ"
  description="Websites from $3,800 + GST, care from $149 a month + GST. One written proposal for your exact site, no surprises, and a love it or leave it guarantee."
>
  <BreadcrumbSchema
    slot="head"
    items={[
      { name: 'Home', url: 'https://yourhq.co.nz/' },
      { name: 'Pricing', url: 'https://yourhq.co.nz/pricing' }
    ]}
  />
  <FAQSchema slot="head" />
  <Navbar client:load />

  <main class="bg-bone font-sans text-carbon min-h-screen selection:bg-terracotta selection:text-white overflow-hidden">

    <!-- ============================================================
         HEADER
    ============================================================ -->
    <section class="pt-24 md:pt-32 pb-24 border-b border-carbon/10">
      <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="max-w-4xl">
          <span class="font-mono text-[10px] md:text-xs font-medium uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-deepGreen mb-6 flex items-center gap-3">
            <span class="w-8 h-[1px] bg-deepGreen"></span> Pricing
          </span>
          <h1 class="font-display font-bold text-hero uppercase leading-none tracking-tight mb-8">
            Two numbers.<br/>
            <span class="font-serif italic text-terracotta normal-case font-normal">The rest is a conversation.</span>
          </h1>
          <p class="font-sans text-subhead text-softGrey max-w-2xl">
            No tiers to compare. No calculator. No package-picking.<br/>
            We talk, then I send you one proposal for your exact site. One price, in writing.
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============================================================
         THE NUMBERS
    ============================================================ -->
    <section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-white border-b border-carbon/10">
      <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <div class="grid lg:grid-cols-12 gap-12 lg:gap-16 items-start">

          <div class="lg:col-span-6">
            <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-display uppercase leading-[1.05] tracking-tight text-carbon mb-8">
              Builds from $3,800 + GST.<br/>
              <span class="font-serif italic text-softGrey normal-case font-normal">Care from $149 a month + GST.</span>
            </h2>
            <div class="font-sans text-body text-softGrey space-y-6 max-w-xl">
              <p>Where it lands depends on what we&rsquo;re building. A straightforward site for a trade business and a personal brand with a course attached are different jobs, and pretending one price fits both is how the industry ends up quoting nonsense.</p>
              <p>So I don&rsquo;t make you guess which package you are. You book a 20-minute chat, tell me about your business, and within a couple of days you get a proposal for your site specifically. What it includes, what it costs to build, and what the monthly care number is. One page. No surprises, no upsells buried in the fine print.</p>
            </div>
            <a href={BOOKING_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="mt-10 inline-block bg-carbon text-white px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full font-medium text-sm hover:bg-deepGreen transition-colors duration-300 shadow-subtle">
              Book a Website Chat
            </a>
          </div>

          <div class="lg:col-span-6 flex flex-col gap-6">
            <div class="bg-bone rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-10 border border-carbon/10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-8 justify-between items-start">
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl uppercase tracking-tight text-carbon mb-2">The Build</h3>
                <p class="font-sans text-carbon/75 leading-relaxed text-sm max-w-sm">
                  Your story captured in one conversation, every page written in your voice, built by hand, everything you need to be credible and found.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-left sm:text-right shrink-0">
                <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-softGrey block mb-1">One-time · from</span>
                <p class="font-display font-bold text-3xl text-carbon leading-none">$3,800</p>
                <p class="font-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-softGrey mt-1">NZD + GST</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-bone rounded-3xl p-8 sm:p-10 border border-carbon/10 flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-8 justify-between items-start">
              <div>
                <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl uppercase tracking-tight text-carbon mb-2">Monthly Care</h3>
                <p class="font-sans text-carbon/75 leading-relaxed text-sm max-w-sm">
                  Hosting, security, backups, and the message-me service. Your proposal states your exact number before anything starts.
                </p>
              </div>
              <div class="text-left sm:text-right shrink-0">
                <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-terracotta block mb-1">Ongoing · from</span>
                <p class="font-display font-bold text-3xl text-carbon leading-none">$149<span class="font-sans font-normal text-sm text-softGrey">/mo NZD</span></p>
                <p class="font-mono text-[9px] uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-softGrey mt-1">+ GST</p>
              </div>
            </div>
            <div class="border-l-2 border-terracotta pl-6 py-2">
              <p class="font-serif italic text-lg text-carbon/80 leading-snug">
                The proposal is free, and it&rsquo;s yours either way.<br/>
                If you take it to another developer, it&rsquo;ll be the clearest brief they&rsquo;ve ever received.
              </p>
            </div>
          </div>

        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============================================================
         WHAT THE BUILD FEE COVERS
    ============================================================ -->
    <section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-bone border-b border-carbon/10">
      <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 md:gap-16 items-start">
        <div class="md:col-span-5">
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-display uppercase leading-[1.05] tracking-tight text-carbon">
            Everything you need to be credible and found.
            <span class="font-serif italic text-terracotta normal-case font-normal block mt-2">As standard.</span>
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-7 font-sans text-body text-softGrey space-y-6 max-w-2xl">
          <p class="font-medium text-carbon">Everything in the build exists so you never have to think about your website again. That&rsquo;s the actual product.</p>
          <p>I didn&rsquo;t build the standard package around what&rsquo;s cheap to include. I built it around one question: what do you actually need, right now, to be credible online and get found?</p>
          <p>So your build comes with a blog, because Google and AI tools reward businesses that publish and punish sites that never change. It comes with your Google Business Profile set up properly, because that&rsquo;s where local search happens. An enquiry form straight to your inbox. Email capture you own. Your socials embedded. Built to load in under a second and structured so both Google and AI tools can read it and cite it.</p>
          <p>None of that is an add-on. None of it costs extra. It&rsquo;s the build, because you need it. Charging separately for the things a website can&rsquo;t be credible without is how the industry got its reputation.</p>
          <p>And underneath all of it: your story captured in one conversation, every page written in your voice and approved by you before I build, your content raided from everything you&rsquo;ve already made so you send me nothing, and your domain registered in your name from day one.</p>
          <p class="font-serif italic text-accent text-carbon/80">There&rsquo;s no starter tier and nothing held back for a higher price. Anything less isn&rsquo;t worth putting my name on.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============================================================
         WHAT THE MONTHLY COVERS
    ============================================================ -->
    <section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-white border-b border-carbon/10">
      <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 md:gap-16 items-start">
        <div class="md:col-span-5">
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-display uppercase leading-[1.05] tracking-tight text-carbon">
            This isn&rsquo;t a hosting fee.
            <span class="font-serif italic text-softGrey normal-case font-normal block mt-2">It&rsquo;s me, looking after your site.</span>
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-7 font-sans text-body text-softGrey space-y-6 max-w-2xl">
          <p>Hosting, security, backups, all running quietly underneath. But the real product is the message-me service. New prices? Message me. New testimonial? Message me. New photo from a job? Message me. It&rsquo;s live within a day, usually faster.</p>
          <p>The monthly starts at $149 and scales with what your site actually does. A simple site that anchors your credibility costs less to look after than one running bookings and payments. Your proposal states your exact number before anything starts, and it doesn&rsquo;t move without a conversation first.</p>
          <div class="border-l-2 border-terracotta pl-6 py-2">
            <p class="text-carbon/80">Last month Brad from Carve Earthworks sent through a list of copy tweaks for the site I built him six months ago. Live the same day. That&rsquo;s what the monthly buys.</p>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============================================================
         THE GUARANTEE
    ============================================================ -->
    <section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-carbon text-bone border-b border-carbon">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-display uppercase leading-[1.05] tracking-tight text-white mb-8">
          Love it <span class="font-serif italic text-white/60 normal-case font-normal">or leave it.</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="font-sans text-body text-bone/80 space-y-6 max-w-xl mx-auto text-left">
          <p>I build the complete site before your subscription starts. You see the finished thing on a private preview link. Not a mockup, not a concept. The actual site, on your phone, shareable with anyone whose opinion you want.</p>
          <p>Love it, we go live and the monthly starts. Don&rsquo;t love it, full refund of your setup fee, minus card processing (about 3%) and any domain costs already paid.</p>
          <p class="font-medium text-white text-center pt-2">No love, no commitment. That&rsquo;s the deal.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============================================================
         ALREADY HAVE A SITE? THE AUDIT
    ============================================================ -->
    <section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-surface border-b border-carbon/10">
      <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 md:gap-16 items-center">
        <div class="md:col-span-6">
          <span class="font-mono text-badge uppercase text-terracotta block mb-4">The Other Door</span>
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-display uppercase leading-[1.05] tracking-tight text-carbon mb-6">
            Start with the<br/>
            <span class="font-serif italic text-terracotta normal-case font-normal">Website Audit.</span>
          </h2>
          <p class="font-sans text-body text-softGrey max-w-lg mb-6">
            If you&rsquo;ve already got a site and want the evidence before you decide anything, the audit is the place to start. Every page scored, a recommended new structure, and page-by-page copy rewritten in your voice. One document, five working days.
          </p>
          <p class="font-sans text-body text-carbon max-w-lg mb-8">
            <strong>$997 + GST, one-time.</strong> Build with me within 90 days and the full $997 comes off your build price.
          </p>
          <a href="/website-audit" class="inline-block bg-carbon text-white px-8 py-3.5 rounded-full font-medium text-sm hover:bg-deepGreen transition-colors duration-300 shadow-subtle">
            See the Website Audit &rarr;
          </a>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-6">
          <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-10 border border-carbon/10 shadow-subtle max-w-md md:ml-auto">
            <div class="flex items-baseline justify-between border-b border-carbon/10 pb-6 mb-6">
              <span class="font-display font-bold text-5xl tracking-tight text-carbon">$997</span>
              <span class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-softGrey text-right">NZD + GST<br/>One-time</span>
            </div>
            <ul class="space-y-3 font-sans text-sm text-carbon/80">
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-terracotta shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#10003;</span> Every page scored, site score out of 50</li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-terracotta shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#10003;</span> What&rsquo;s working, what&rsquo;s holding you back</li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-terracotta shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#10003;</span> A recommended new structure for your site</li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-terracotta shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#10003;</span> Page-by-page copy rewritten in your voice</li>
              <li class="flex gap-3"><span class="text-terracotta shrink-0" aria-hidden="true">&#10003;</span> $997 credit toward a build, within 90 days</li>
            </ul>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============================================================
         WHEN YOUR SITE NEEDS TO DO MORE
    ============================================================ -->
    <section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-bone border-b border-carbon/10">
      <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 grid md:grid-cols-12 gap-12 md:gap-16 items-start">
        <div class="md:col-span-5">
          <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-display uppercase leading-[1.05] tracking-tight text-carbon">
            If your business needs it,
            <span class="font-serif italic text-terracotta normal-case font-normal block mt-2">we talk about it.</span>
          </h2>
        </div>
        <div class="md:col-span-7 font-sans text-body text-softGrey space-y-6 max-w-2xl">
          <p>Bookings, email platforms, Stripe payments for services and digital products, content automation, even a full course platform or a members&rsquo; space. If the conversation shows your business needs it, it goes in your proposal with a fixed price next to it. You only ever pay for what your site actually needs, and you&rsquo;ll never discover an add-on you were supposed to know about.</p>
          <p>The one line I hold: physical products with inventory and shipping belong on Shopify, and I&rsquo;ll tell you so and point you to someone good.</p>
          <div class="bg-white rounded-3xl p-8 md:p-10 border border-carbon/10 shadow-subtle">
            <span class="font-mono text-badge uppercase text-deepGreen block mb-3">The extra worth its own page</span>
            <h3 class="font-display font-bold text-xl uppercase tracking-tight text-carbon mb-3">The Learning Hub</h3>
            <p class="font-sans text-sm text-softGrey leading-relaxed mb-6">
              A full course platform on your own domain, with student logins, progress tracking, and Stripe checkout. Built by someone who spent 15 years in learning design before building websites.
            </p>
            <a href="/learning-hub" class="font-mono text-[10px] uppercase tracking-[0.15em] text-carbon border-b border-carbon/20 pb-1 hover:border-carbon transition-colors">
              See the Learning Hub &rarr;
            </a>
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============================================================
         OWNERSHIP AND EXIT
    ============================================================ -->
    <section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-deepGreen text-bone border-b border-carbon/20">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-display uppercase leading-[1.05] tracking-tight text-white mb-8">
          Nothing held hostage. <span class="font-serif italic text-terracotta normal-case font-normal">Ever.</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="font-sans text-body text-bone/85 space-y-6 max-w-xl mx-auto">
          <p>Your domain is registered in your name from day one. Your content, your design, your data, all yours unconditionally.</p>
          <p>Pause anytime; your site stays live and secure, no penalty. Leave with 30 days notice and you get a full clean export of everything. Your next developer gets a complete codebase, not a ransom note.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============================================================
         PRICING FAQ
    ============================================================ -->
    <section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-surface border-b border-carbon/10">
      <div class="max-w-screen-xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8">
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-display uppercase leading-[1.05] tracking-tight text-carbon mb-16">
          Pricing <span class="font-serif italic text-terracotta normal-case font-normal">FAQ.</span>
        </h2>
        <div class="grid md:grid-cols-2 gap-x-16 gap-y-10 max-w-5xl">
          {faqs.map((f) => (
            <div class="border-t border-carbon/10 pt-6">
              <h3 class="font-sans font-medium text-carbon mb-2">{f.q}</h3>
              <p class="font-sans text-sm text-softGrey leading-relaxed">{f.a}</p>
            </div>
          ))}
        </div>
        <p class="font-sans text-xs text-softGrey mt-16 max-w-2xl border-t border-carbon/10 pt-6">
          <strong class="text-carbon/70">Tax note:</strong> monthly fees are typically operating expenses, deductible in the year you pay them. Your setup fee may be treated differently. Check with your accountant.
        </p>
      </div>
    </section>

    <!-- ============================================================
         FINAL CTA
    ============================================================ -->
    <section class="py-24 md:py-32 bg-bone text-center px-4">
      <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto">
        <span class="font-mono text-badge uppercase text-softGrey block mb-6">The Next Step</span>
        <h2 class="font-display font-bold text-display uppercase leading-[1.05] tracking-tight mb-8 text-carbon">
          Twenty minutes<br/>
          <span class="font-serif italic text-terracotta normal-case font-normal">gets you a number.</span>
        </h2>
        <p class="font-sans text-body text-softGrey max-w-xl mx-auto mb-10">
          Book the chat, tell me about your business, and you&rsquo;ll have a written proposal for your exact site within days. Rather not talk? Send the contact form instead and we&rsquo;ll do it all in writing. Same proposal either way, no prep, no pitch, no obligation.
        </p>
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center">
          <a href={BOOKING_URL} target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer" class="inline-block bg-carbon text-white px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-medium text-sm hover:bg-deepGreen transition-colors duration-300 shadow-subtle">
            Book a Website Chat
          </a>
          <a href="/contact" class="inline-block bg-transparent text-carbon border border-carbon/20 px-10 py-4 rounded-full font-medium text-sm hover:border-carbon transition-colors duration-300">
            Or start with the form
          </a>
        </div>
        <p class="font-sans text-sm text-softGrey mt-6">Or just message me: {PHONE}.</p>
      </div>
    </section>

  </main>

  <Footer />
</Layout>
